misux.io.http.cover
Class GetCover

java.lang.Object
  misux.io.http.cover.GetCover
Direct Known Subclasses:
GetCoverAmazon, GetCoverFromAll, GetCoverGoogle
public abstract class GetCover
extends java.lang.Object

This abstract class implements methods to download and save covers. The name of the interpret and album are needed. It can download one cover or more.

Author:
DSIW
